text: Kadis-kot is a fictional board game in the TV show Star Trek: Voyager. It is played on a six-sided board with three sets of coloured stones. The characters of Naomi Wildman and Seven of Nine played the game sometimes, after the events of the episode "Infinite Regress". ==Other websites== * A summary of the game at Memory Alpha Category:Star Trek: Voyager Category:Board games
title: Kadis-kot
